"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1930099-Olympics-tennis-Taylor-Fritz-Paris-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Taylor Fritzis set to play three matches at theOlympicson Wednesday with the schedule having thrown up a gruelling run of fixtures.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 133, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 26-year-old is representing the USA in three events after being named in their squad for the men's singles, men's doubles and mixed doubles.\", \"from\": 134, \"to\": 278, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 170, \"end\": 173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.943463132734411, \"rank\": 0.051814135150962, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fritz, will face Lorenzo Musetti in the third round of the men's singles after beating Alexander Bublik and Jack Draper in his first two matches.\", \"from\": 280, \"to\": 425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 297, \"end\": 312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lorenzo_Musetti\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lorenzo Musetti\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lorenzo_Musetti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lorenzo_Musetti\"}, {\"begin\": 367, \"end\": 383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexander_Bublik\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alexander Bublik\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexander_Bublik\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexander_Bublik\"}, {\"begin\": 388, \"end\": 399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Draper_(tennis)\", \"score\": 0.9926967693033829, \"rank\": 0.007352941176469691, \"text\": \"Jack Draper\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Draper_(tennis)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Draper_(tennis)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the men's doubles, he will partner Tommy Paul against the Dutch pairing of Robin Haase and Jean-Julien Rojer in the second round.\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 558, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 464, \"end\": 474, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Paul\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.484413766532059e-17, \"text\": \"Tommy Paul\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Paul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Paul\"}, {\"begin\": 487, \"end\": 492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.7188042511577061, \"rank\": 0.3551475213189832, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 504, \"end\": 515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robin_Haase\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Robin Haase\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robin_Haase\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robin_Haase\"}, {\"begin\": 520, \"end\": 537, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Julien_Rojer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jean-Julien Rojer\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Julien_Rojer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Julien_Rojer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He will also be in action with Coco Gauff in the quarter-finals of the mixed doubles against Argentina duo Maximo Gonzalez and Nadia Podoroska.\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 703, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 591, \"end\": 601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Coco Gauff\", 