 Roland Garros.\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 1100, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1086, \"end\": 1099, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"score\": 0.9999999999263309, \"rank\": 7.362576371954306e-11, \"text\": \"Roland Garros\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fritz will return to the same court for the third match of the day in the men's doubles before heading to Court Mathieu to play in the last eight of the mixed doubles.\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1268, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He will only have a few hours to recover before playing three matches in quick succession after securing a comeback victory over Draper in the men's singles on Tuesday.\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1438, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He dropped the first set but managed to keep his composure, battling hard in scorching conditions to win the next two and seal the match.\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1576, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Murray delays retirement again as Brit reaches Olympics quarter-final with Evans  Do not miss:Calls to 'protect' Emma Raducanu ramp up as Brit sent warning over coaches  Do not miss:Show your colours and get Team GB's official kit for the Paris Olympics  Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1578, \"to\": 1887, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1590, \"end\": 1596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.695917683577217e-32, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 1665, \"end\": 1670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.6640350511492138, \"rank\": 0.5059446007695262, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}, {\"begin\": 1703, \"end\": 1716, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Raducanu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emma Raducanu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Raducanu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Raducanu\"}, {\"begin\": 1798, \"end\": 1805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9884226588528944, \"rank\": 0.01171223439528364, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 1888, \"to\": 1958, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1952, \"end\": 1957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998967724, \"rank\": 1.0324911725835724e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 2063, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2033, \"end\": 2045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9968661062493619, \"rank\": 0.0031437453746283105, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2118, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The heat in Paris has soared to 35 degrees Celsius at times, with Olympic bosses giving players a 10-minute break between the second and third sets.\", \"from